HEADING
Note
    Nested note

- task that is not started
X - task that is done
O - task that is actively being worked on
W - task that is waiting for something
- task with meta information(meta information here, due date, links to websites, etc)

- parent task
    - nested task
        - another nested task, nested levels can be infinite. All items(tasks, headings, notes, etc.) can have nested children.